metadata.name: Aquanica
metadata.description: In the depths of the ocean, the place where life originated, there are many secrets and dangers.Perhaps from here we will begin our journey with you.Aquanica is the daughter of the king of the oceans and seas.Her gaze is charming, and her smile is mesmerizing...Rarely have any of the people managed to see her, but they say that to see her is a great success)
